                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note states that the Ms. was written in the time of King Täklä Giyorgis (r. several periods between 1779-1800) and Prince Wäldä Lǝʿul (d. 1767?). The latter also donated land to the church. 
The note is written in red by the same hand that inserted the name of "prince" (mäsfǝn) Wäldä Lǝʿul in erasures.</p>
